{"tid":675690,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"今日做咩鬼月蝕咩？","createTime":"2018-05-23T17:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T17:53:56.000Z","uid":118884,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"67dbd24c3f03107c7aea60f6d0e63326c7c6ccc2","tid":675690,"uid":118884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T17:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/014452_ba810072aaa0565ae5b788773931fcf3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F014452_ba810072aaa0565ae5b788773931fcf3.png&h=ff8031fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夜媽媽悶悶地諗著上天台曬下月光<br />\n望望下<br />\n見到個月亮紅色既<br />\n今日月蝕咩<br />\n有無巴絲打都見到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02799f18f3e4b6484d194c766eef7253d86e3cb6","tid":675690,"uid":118884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T17:53:56.000Z","msg":"可能影得唔清楚<br />\n但如果係街<br />\n同窗口望出去<br />\n應該都會見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n突然見到天文現像<br />\n都幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}